---
title: Teppanyaki-Inspired Striploin Steak with Yum-Yum Sauce and Toasted Sesame Veggies
description: Take me to the teppanyaki! Seared and sizzling steak with wholesome mixed veggies gets a Japanese-influenced twist! To dip and drizzle, we've got a savoury soy-mirin and toasted sesame teriyaki along with a yum-yum sauce that is 'yum yum', as promised!
